      "text": "Issue was previously marked as resolved, but manual testing shows the changeset list problem persists. The plan approval works and feature branches are created, but `exactl changeset list` still returns empty.\n\n### Reproduction from Latest Test\n\n```bash\nexactl changeset list\n✅ changeset.list: changesets\n   count: 0\n   message: No changesets found\n\n# But in portal repo:\ngit branch\n\n* feat/request-a300d5a5-a300d5a5\n  master\n```\n\nThe changeset listing logic needs to be investigated further.\n\n## Resolution\n\n### Fixed on 2026-01-22\n\nRoot causes identified and resolved:",
